Package: tQTLExperiment
Title: SummarizedExperiment Interface for the tensorQTL eQTL Mapping Tool
Version: 0.1.28
Authors@R: c(
    person("Vincent", "Carey", email = "stvjc@channing.harvard.edu",
           role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Claude", "Sonnet", role = "eng",
           comment = "Anthropic AI assistant"))
Description: Provides a SummarizedExperiment-derived container,
    tQTLExperiment, for managing phenotype, covariate, and genotype data
    for use with the tensorQTL GPU-accelerated eQTL mapping tool. Genotype
    data is represented lazily via BEDMatrix. A runTQTL() method handles
    file I/O and invokes the tensorQTL CLI (python -m tensorqtl), returning
    results as GRanges objects. On Apple Silicon, the MPS (Metal Performance
    Shaders) backend is used automatically when available.
